# This directory is populated by the C++ build step.
#
# Run the following from the project root to generate these files:
#
#   cd cpp-module
#   ./build.sh debug
#
# Output files placed here:
#   demo.js        — Emscripten JavaScript glue code
#   demo.wasm      — WebAssembly binary
#   demo.wasm.map  — Source map for C++ debugging in WeChat DevTools
